events.name: EV001アクティナの巫女からの依頼1-4

parameters:
Will you enter the innermost part of the Demon Bride Ancos'
altar?
Clea (Let's prepare first and then do it.)

Thief Nora: The person who told me about the dragon's
whereabouts before was happily calling me a 'subhuman'...

Thief Nora: I have a bad feeling about this place, like
something scary is going to happen deep inside.
Clea: Don't worry, we're right behind you.

Mage Relm: Clea-san is right! There's no way we'll lose to
an old-fashioned witch like her!

Priestess Sophia: Don't worry, if it looks bad, we can
escape and leave it to the others.
Thief Nora: Somehow, I'm starting to feel okay!
Clea: I'm glad, let's go in.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

events.name: EV09アクティナの巫女からの依頼1-7

parameters:
Demon Bride Ancos: Haa... haa... What happened... My magical
power was instantly wiped out...

Demon Bride Ancos: What is that? What is it... I finally
obtained a body, and now... in a place like this...
Demon Bride Ancos: I can't let it end like this--

Demon Bride Ancos: Huh...? My arm... why, it's gone, my arm,
my arm!
Bard: I left you because I was hiding inside the crystal.

Bard: If that comes out, the situation will change. If you
return to your original place, you will no longer be the
target.

Demon Bride Ancos: Hehehe, ahahaha, don't make fun of me! I
am Ancos, the Demon Bride Ancos!

Demon Bride Ancos: I will shatter the false empire and
establish a complete empire that worships Amador--

Bard: Oh, small sun of Sol... I have passed judgment upon
the fools in your name.

Bard: As I thought, you were someone who couldn't give up. I
can't forgive those who go against reason.

Do you want to restart from the battle? If you choose No, it
will result in a game over.
